    {"type":"text","id":"artifact_persist_t","x":96,"y":1450,"width":1652,"height":260,"text":"Concrete artifacts + contracts\n.lily/session.json -> active_agent, active_persona, skill_snapshot, conversation_state\n.lily/config.yaml -> checkpointer, memory_tooling, consolidation, compaction, security sandbox\n.lily/checkpoints/checkpointer.sqlite -> conversation thread checkpoints\n.lily/memory/personality_memory.json + task_memory.json + evidence_memory.json\n.lily/db/security.sqlite -> approvals, provenance, language_policy_cache\n.lily/jobs/*.job.yaml -> validated JobSpec; .lily/runs/<job_id>/run_*/{run_receipt.json,summary.md,events.jsonl}\n\nSkill loading evidence\ndiscover_candidates(bundled/workspace/user) -> resolve_precedence -> parse_skill_markdown -> eligibility/tool checks -> hashed SkillSnapshot\n\nPlugin hardening evidence\nSecurityHashService.compute -> SecurityLanguagePolicy(AST) -> preflight signature scan -> HITL approval -> DockerPluginRunner","originalText":"Concrete artifacts + contracts\n.lily/session.json -> active_agent, active_persona, skill_snapshot, conversation_state\n.lily/config.yaml -> checkpointer, memory_tooling, consolidation, compaction, security sandbox\n.lily/checkpoints/checkpointer.sqlite -> conversation thread checkpoints\n.lily/memory/personality_memory.json + task_memory.json + evidence_memory.json\n.lily/db/security.sqlite -> approvals, provenance, language_policy_cache\n.lily/jobs/*.job.yaml -> validated JobSpec; .lily/runs/<job_id>/run_*/{run_receipt.json,summary.md,events.jsonl}\n\nSkill loading evidence\ndiscover_candidates(bundled/workspace/user) -> resolve_precedence -> parse_skill_markdown -> eligibility/tool checks -> hashed SkillSnapshot\n\nPlugin hardening evidence\nSecurityHashService.compute -> SecurityLanguagePolicy(AST) -> preflight signature scan -> HITL approval -> DockerPluginRunner","fontSize":17,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#2ECC71","backgroundColor":"transparent"